        {
            "title": "日本家庭支出意外下降 流露內需疲軟跡象",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 日本居民意外削減了開支，為六個月來首次，表明在<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:日本央行;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/日本央行\">日本央行</a>準備於本月晚些時候考慮提高借貸成本之際，國內需求脆弱。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本總務省周五公佈，經通膨因素調整後，10月家庭支出同比下降3%，交通和住房支出下降是主因。經濟學家此前預期為成長1%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kGxWMm4E_EGupetwNheHmw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/a525f62587ebc2958fd221f7c320f350\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本央行想要實現經濟良性循環的目標，即薪資成長推動需求驅動的價格上漲，而私人支出是其中的一項關鍵組成部分。日本國內消費已連續三個季度成長，不過步伐不大。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本央行在其10月展望報告中表示，私人消費短期內可能基本持平，之後將逐步恢復「溫和成長趨勢，伴隨著員工收入的持續成長」。在日本央行邁向再次加息之際，周五數據的下滑將為形勢增添一重複雜性，但預計不會改變央行路徑。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-8fafed61-2f83-3c02-9767-d48882b0cb38-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Japan’s Household Outlays Fall in Fragile Domestic Demand Sign</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Paul Jackson.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E6%94%AF%E5%87%BA%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D-%E6%B5%81%E9%9C%B2%E5%85%A7%E9%9C%80%E7%96%B2%E8%BB%9F%E8%B7%A1%E8%B1%A1-011823525.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-05 10:25:46",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "地方政府平台從非銀機構高息借債 中國影子銀行捲土重來",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 中國對地方政府舉債的治理整頓，迫使即使是一些最富裕省份的國有實體也不得不轉向成本高昂的非銀行貸款機構獲取資金，這種無奈之舉卻正在金融體系一個不甚透明的角落裡積聚著風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這種借貸標志著中國的影子銀行市場捲土重來；與傳統貸款機構相比，這個市場受到的監管較為寬鬆，過去幾年為了降低風險，則收緊了管控。據知情人士透露，自9月以來，包括山東在內多個省份的地方政府旗下產業投資機構和融資平台，已累計從信託公司和租賃公司借款數十億美元。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0c33d7a9-ae22-3792-bb1c-f124df427319-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士表示，貸款收取的利率為8%或更高——是在債券市場融資成本的三倍還多。因信息並未公開，他們要求匿名。構成中國影子銀行體系的金融機構願意提供資金，部分原因是在低利率環境下它們面臨資產短缺的問題。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此類貸款需求成長，反映了中國政府為阻止各省通過所謂地方政府融資平台積累債務而採取行動所帶來的後果。這項行動阻塞了各省獲得低成本融資的渠道，例如常規銀行貸款和發行債券，導致這個世界第二大經濟體的投資減少。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">法國巴黎銀行首席中國經濟學家榮靜表示，如果財政紀律不那麼嚴格，富裕地區的平台就不必求助如此昂貴的融資方式了；化解隱性債務和收緊財政紀律的舉措可能是基礎設施投資大幅下滑的一個關鍵原因。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"投資下滑\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/0PZ52bgRdtDqQWoaFU5CEg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/58c5c23124089445bdf66a116fd2a036\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">投資下滑</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國財政部、國家金融監督管理總局和山東省政府新聞處均未回應彭博尋求評論的請求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Shadow Banks Back in Spotlight With Loans for Ailing Firms</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Yuling Yang、Dingmin Zhang.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
